summary: Background in research and education, after a switch to consultancy, work on financial sector regulation and supervision at Dutch Ministry of Finance and the the Dutch Central Bank and the last couple of years Director of Foreign Financial Affairs and deputy Treasurer General at the Dutch Treasury. Currently working on Energy Policy as deputy Director General for Climate & Energy and Director of Energy Markets.
